org.afplib.afplib

Interface BeginSegmentCommand

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BeginSegmentCommandImpl

    public interface BeginSegmentCommand
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'Begin Segment Command'.

    The following features are supported:

    • LENGTH
    • NAME
    • FLAG1
    • FLAG2
    • SEGL
    • PSNAME

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getBeginSegmentCommand()
